## MuPDF

MuPDF is not bundled, linked, downloaded, or required by the Milestone 0 default
build. The real MuPDF integration is deferred to Milestone 1.

When `real-mupdf` is enabled in a future build, this file must be regenerated to
include the exact MuPDF version, source location, license choice, bundled
notices, local patches, and corresponding-source instructions.

## Rust Toolchain

The Milestone 0 default workspace build currently depends only on the Rust
standard library and local workspace crates.

Optional post-M0 features may add third-party crates to `Cargo.lock`. They are
not part of the default M0 resolve graph unless their feature is enabled. Before
any optional feature becomes a required build or shipped distribution target,
this file must be regenerated to include that feature's exact third-party
dependency notices.

## GUI Font Assets

The optional `pdbg-app/gui` feature bundles the following Open Font License
fonts for a reproducible debugger UI:

- Inter v4.1, from <https://github.com/rsms/inter/releases/tag/v4.1>,
  licensed under the SIL Open Font License 1.1. The bundled font file is
  `crates/pdbg-app/assets/fonts/InterVariable.ttf`; the copied license text is
  `crates/pdbg-app/assets/licenses/Inter-OFL.txt`.
- JetBrains Mono v2.304, from
  <https://github.com/JetBrains/JetBrainsMono/releases/tag/v2.304>, licensed
  under the SIL Open Font License 1.1. The bundled font file is
  `crates/pdbg-app/assets/fonts/JetBrainsMono-Regular.ttf`; the copied license
  text is `crates/pdbg-app/assets/licenses/JetBrainsMono-OFL.txt`.
